@startuml
title Manage Schedule - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Veterinarian" as Vet
participant "Web SPA" as Web
participant "api-gateway" as Gateway
participant "vets-service\nWorkScheduleController" as Controller
participant "WorkScheduleService" as Service
database "vets.work_schedule_slots" as DB

Vet -> Web: Edit working hours / unavailable slot
Web -> Gateway: PUT /api/v1/vets/me/schedule
Gateway -> Controller: route with VET role
Controller -> Service: replaceSchedule(vetId, request)
Service -> DB: validate overlaps and save slots
alt valid schedule
  Controller --> Web: WorkScheduleSlotResponse
else overlap or invalid time
  Controller --> Web: ProblemDetail 400
end
@enduml
